name: Perform evaluation on a preconfigured inference unit without essential evaluation criteria

steps.name: Given a valid, preconfigured inference unit for tabular multiclass classification
And an evaluation plan file for tabular multiclass classification with no evaluation tasks and no report spec
And a dataset reference path_to_dataset
And a uuid my_unique_identifier for the inference unit evaluation
And with local report file location
When we run inference unit evaluation
Then a successful result indicating all criteria passed is computed
Then the precision metric for class name 0 is calculated to be 0.36
Then the recall metric for class name 0 is calculated to be 0.45
Then the f1 metric for class name 0 is calculated to be 0.4
Then the rocauc metric for class name 0 is calculated to be 0.7
Then the precision metric for class name 1 is calculated to be 0.25
Then the recall metric for class name 1 is calculated to be 0.2
Then the f1 metric for class name 1 is calculated to be 0.22
Then the rocauc metric for class name 1 is calculated to be 0.43
Then the precision metric for class name 2 is calculated to be 0.25
Then the recall metric for class name 2 is calculated to be 0.22
Then the f1 metric for class name 2 is calculated to be 0.24
Then the rocauc metric for class name 2 is calculated to be 0.59
Then the precision metric for class name 3 is calculated to be 0.27
Then the recall metric for class name 3 is calculated to be 0.29
Then the f1 metric for class name 3 is calculated to be 0.28
Then the rocauc metric for class name 3 is calculated to be 0.55
Then macro average of the precision metric is calculated to be 0.28
Then macro average of the recall metric is calculated to be 0.29
Then macro average of the f1 metric is calculated to be 0.28
Then macro average of the rocauc metric is calculated to be 0.56
Then macro average of the acc metric is calculated to be 0.29
